Class Reservation

  • java.lang.Object
    • Reservation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Reservation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a Reservation object to reserve a table. It reserves a Table at a particular date and time for a customer. Reservation object also tracks the number of pax coming, and if the customer arrived during his reservation timing.
    Since:
    2021-11-5
    See Also:
